data.description: Brand New Roof! Welcome to this beautiful, updated 2 master bedroom, 2 full bath waterfront home located in the desirable community of Fresh Meadows. This property offers a split floor plan with a large living room/dining area featuring 11 ft vaulted ceilings and pocket glass sliding doors to the spacious Florida room. The master bedroom features an en suite full bathroom and large walk-in closet, also with an 11 ft vaulted ceiling and pocket glass sliding doors to the Florida room. The eat in kitchen offers brand new shaker style cabinets, countertops, backsplash and stainless steel appliances with a glass sliding door to the Florida room. The rest of the home has a spacious second master bedroom with an en suite full bathroom, a large walk-in closet, a laundry room and a 2-car attached garage. A few additional features include a brand new roof (November 2023) fresh neutral paint throughout home, Florida room, garage walls and floor, tile throughout, all new ceiling fans and light fixtures and both bathrooms offer new countertops, toilets, undermount sinks and fixtures. This home is a minute’s walk to the community pool, tennis court, playground and public parking and just a short drive to public schools, shopping, restaurants, local beaches and highways. This move in ready home has everything…….all its missing is you! Schedule your private showing today! Seller will contribute $2,500. towards buyer's closing costs.
